title: Psychopomp's Gate
alt: A peacock standing in a disembodied doorway, in cloudy fog. Stones and geometric shapes are barely discernable in the background.

title: Cottage of Tranquility
alt: A small cottage made out of a snail shell, with round portal-type windows set in a grassy meadow with bare trees. An armadillo is browsing in front of it.

title: Childhood Memories
alt: Two smiling young girls are standing behind a large swan in a simulated antique photo with indescipherable handwriting overlaid on it.

title: Forgotten Shrine of Lepidoptera
alt: An old dressmaker's dummy with a lightbulb in place of a head is in the foreground of a wooded environment with ladyslippers and other wildflowers. Butterflies and moths are flying toward the lightbulb's glow.

title: Bride of Dumpty
alt: An egg-headed girl in a bridal dress is standing in the foreground with a rocking horse and broken eggshells at her feet. There is a full moon and a stone wall in the background.

title: Baba Yaga's Place
alt: An egg hut with a thatched roof walks on spindly chicken legs sticking out of the hut's supportive nest. The backdrop is a moody sky with bare trees and a grazing goat.

title: Anatomy of Loneliness
alt: The burnt torso of a plastic doll is overlaid with textures and branches.

title: An Afternoon Chat
alt: Two women from the American Civil War era are sitting at a garden table that supports a small vase of flowers. There is an overlay of a handwritten letter and dried roses and petals.

title: A Man and his Monkey
alt: A monocled, bald man sits for a daguerratype portrait with a monkey on his shoulder. The image is heavily textured with roots and handwriting.

title: A Life of Waiting
alt: A rusted, empty bed without a mattress sits in an abandoned room with an old tattered vinyl chair off to the side. A bare lightbulb hangs in the foreground.

title: Untitled
alt: A lamp post appears to grow out of a hollow dead tree trunk at night. There is a barred owl sitting on the tree trunk while a rabbit grazes on tall grass and purple flowers in front of it.

title: Darkness
alt: A moody, heavily textured portrait of a dark-haired man with his face half in shadow.

title: Dwelling
alt: An egg house with a thatched roof sits behind a fence made of forks sticking tines-up is in the foreground. There is a blue sky and the house features topiaries to either side of the heavy wooden door.

title: Echo Reborn
alt: A lonely black and white image featuring a bird skull at the top and a possum jawbone at the bottom. There is a large, dark tree in the background and the white border features handwriting around the perimeter of the image.

title: Exiles from Fable
alt: A bird-headed girl in a light blue dress is standing next to an ornately carved tall red velvet chair with a green frog sitting in it. There are keys with butterfly wings perched on top of the chair while a brown rat stands on their hind legs in the foreground.

title: Family Portrait
alt: A somber, sepia-toned portrait of a family of three. The father and mother are holding a toddler. There are three skulls superimposed over the bottom of the image.
